items.content_html:
Summary

Remove data about Error.prototype.toSource (non-standard and obsolete). This is part of mdn/content#15580.

Test results and supporting details

  1. Error.prototype.toSource was removed from Firefox (as shown in BCD and confirmed by testing) and Firefox Android (as tested). Tested with jsconsole.com and the folloqing:
    • 'toString' in Error.prototype returns true
    • 'toSource' in Error.prototype returns false

Related issues

mdn/content#15580
items.title: Remove Error.toSource

items.content_html:
Summary

Mark CSS ::grammar-error and ::spelling-error pseudo-elements as experimental. No browsers have implemented them.
